zKTm","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recvTmyz68pJ75SuN","ref":"Ps.80.1","text":"Give ear, O Shepherd of Israel, thou that leadest Joseph like a flock; thou that dwellest between the cherubims, shine forth."},{"id":"recR1cD1QvoPkMCXw","ref":"Ps.80.2","text":"Before Ephraim and Benjamin and Manasseh stir up thy strength, and come and save us."},{"id":"rec8ysbh0Jt7Ge2s6","ref":"Ps.80.3","text":"Turn us again, O God, and cause thy face to shine; and we shall be saved."},{"id":"recBr8PT9DKK12ETk","ref":"Ps.80.4","text":"O LORD God of hosts, how long wilt thou be angry against the prayer of thy people?"},{"id":"rec6TZ1QmVxRJ0y9n","ref":"Ps.80.5","text":"Thou feedest them with the bread of tears; and givest them tears to drink in great measure."},{"id":"recXWNMnXMPylzKib","ref":"Ps.80.6","text":"Thou makest us a strife unto our neighbours: and our enemies laugh among themselves."},{"id":"rechUFP02vFdiQTiz","ref":"Ps.80.7","text":"Turn us again, O God of hosts, and cause thy face to shine; and we shall be saved."},{"id":"recln4EynYqy9Gx2b","ref":"Ps.80.8","text":"Thou hast brought a vine out of Egypt: thou hast cast out the heathen, and planted it."}]}
